<h1>Hello, {{mentor.first_name}} {{mentor.last_name}}</h1>

<p>{{student.name}} would like to connect with you to chat about:</p>
<ul>
	{{#each session.topics}}
	<li>
		{{this}}
	</li>
	{{/each}}
</ul>
	
<b>
	EpicVisor 1-2-3
</b>

<p>
	<strong>Step 1 for {{mentor.first_name}}</strong> <br> 
	Please visit the EpicSession scheduler and confirm the best time and other details by clicking one of the following times: 
	<br>
</p>
{{#each time_options}}
<p>
	<a href="{{../url}}#/sessions/{{../session.encoded_url}}?selectedTime={{this}}"> {{this}} </a>		
</p>
<br>
{{/each}}
<p>
	Reply all to the student if none of the times specified actually work out.
</p>

<p>
	<b>Step 2: {{student.name}}</b> <br>
	Hi {{student.name}}, <br>
	After {{mentor.first_name}} {{mentor.last_name}} replies back with options, please visit the EpicSession scheduler and confirm the best time: <br>
	<a href="{{url}}#/sessions/{{session.encoded_url}}"> Click on the EpicSession scheduler </a>
</p>
<p>Please confirm within 2 days (The slot will be re-opened after this period).</p>

<p>
	<b>Step 3:</b><br> 
	Connect and have an Epic time together!
</p>
<p>Visit the <a href="{{url}}#/sessions/{{session.encoded_url}}">scheduler</a> to make changes to this session.</p>
